sponsors.title: Mercury Personal Banking
sponsors.content: Mercury just started offering personal banking! I'm already banking with Mercury for business purposes, so getting to bank with them for my personal life makes everything so much simpler. Apply now at https://mercury.com/personal-banking

sponsors.title: Labelbox
sponsors.content: Labelbox can get you robotics and RL data at scale. Labelbox starts by helping you define your ideal data distribution, and then their massive Alignerr network collects frontier-grade data that you can use to train your models. Learn more at https://labelbox.com/dwarkesh
